The most common question I’ve been asked by a potential client is if microlinks can cause their hair to fall or thin out. I love to educate them and talk them through the process. There are a ton of factors into maintaining healthy hair with luxury extensions. The most important ones being:
•Proper installation 
•How the hair is being managed at home (All luxury extensions require the same love and care that you give your real tresses). Meaning BRUSH WEFT TO WEFT DAILY. 
•Scheduling a 6 week tightening
•Scheduling a removal after 12 weeks.

If you are doing what you need to do at home (washing weekly and brushing daily) as well as keep your 6 week maintenance appointment you will not experience any breakage, hair thinning nor hair falling out.

Navigating out of severe depression(caused by grief) was one of the most challenging things I faced in the past calendar year. It was a difficult journey, but I was fortunate to have the luxury of putting my mental health first and taking the necessary steps to get back on track. I was able to create a game plan with my therapist and was able to learn new coping mechanisms to help me manage my depression. I also made sure to take care of my physical health by exercising regularly and eating a balanced diet. Through hard work and dedication, I was able to make a full recovery and am now in a much better place mentally. 

#putyourselffirst #stressmanagement #overcomingdepression #overcominggrief #lifegoeson
